
IMAPStore gasolinebased-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port  993
User gasolinebased@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mutt-wizard-gasolinebased"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gasolinebased-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gasolinebased/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gasolinebased/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel gasolinebased
Expunge Both
Master :gasolinebased-remote:
Slave :gasolinebased-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile


